SAMPLE RUNNING COMMAND:
" pytest Tests/test_LoginPage.py -v --html=./My_HTML_Report_1.html "

- "-v --html=" - use html report plugin
- "." - means put my file into root directory of project
- "My_HTML_Report_1.html" - report name; ".html" part in the end of command is crucial.


2. Next copy "Absolute path" of freshly generated report and paste it into the web browser of your choice.
